<h1>Apply for waste-mgmt project space</h1>
<h3>
As a platform for creatives, we are not only a social network, but also a virtual exhibition space. Every week we introduce you to an up-and-coming Berlin based artist who uses waste-mgmt for his or her work. Apply here to be one of them. Our curatorial team will get in touch with you soon!
</h3>

